Interface CommandArgument

      • tab

        java.util.List<java.lang.String> tab(org.bukkit.command.CommandSender sender,
                                     org.bukkit.command.Command command,

        Executes this argument. Note that the subargs array might exclude the name of this argument.

        Parameters:
        sender - Source of the command
        command - Command which was executed
        alias - Alias of the command which was used
        subargs - Passed command arguments, excluding this, including final partial argument to be completed and command label.
        Returns:
        List of possible completions for the final argument, or null to default to the command executor.
